    "body": "> What if we simply update the change log for betas on the master branch?\r\n\r\nConventional-changelog expects the CHANGELOG to be generated at each release. So we'd need to update on the branch we do betas. Another solution is to regenerate the changelog completly every time we do a release on master.",
